# =============================================================================
# Notes
# =============================================================================
#
# File patterns explanation:
# - **/*.ext matches files with .ext extension in any directory
# - /path/ matches the specific directory
# - /path/* matches files directly in the directory
# - /path/**/* matches files in the directory and all subdirectories
#
# Review requirements:
# - @nguyenquy0710 is the primary maintainer and owner of all code
# - All pull requests will require review from the designated code owners
# - Code owners are automatically notified when files they own are modified
#
